ize:10pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif\">Ng&agrave;y khởi c&ocirc;ng: 19/5/2005</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:inherit\"><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma !important\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif\">Ng&agrave;y kh&aacute;nh th&agrave;nh: 12/03/2011</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:inherit\"><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma !important\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif\">Tổng mức đầu tư: 1.412 tỉ đồng</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:inherit\"><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma !important\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif\">Vốn tự c&oacute;: 476,64 tỉ đồng</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:inherit\"><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma !important\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Vốn vay thương mại</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">:&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">934,21 tỉ đồng</span></span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:inherit\"><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma !important\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>', 0, 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2020-04-25 08:03:00', '2020-05-05 01:32:17');
